metadata.name: Delusion
metadata.description:
Allured by the beauty of the human world, 
tones of a violin fading in and out, 
so faint i try to figure out its meaning.
beckoned to embrace its beautiful sound, i find myself in a different time, 
floating on its strings, absorbed by the tunes.
my breath lost, it feels like i am about to die but unable to, all i can do is feel.
